article.headline: Perkins scores 19 as Pennsylvania tops Dartmouth 80-51 in Ivy League opener
article.description: — Tyler Perkins scored 19 points to help Pennsylvania defeat Dartmouth 80-51 on Saturday in an Ivy League opener.
article.linkText: Perkins scores 19 as Pennsylvania tops Dartmouth 80-51 in Ivy League opener

images.name: Penn Runs Past Dartmouth in League-Opener  - Via Ivy League
images.caption: Freshman Guard Tyler Perkins scored a game-high 19 points with five three-points in Penn's 80-51 win over Dartmouth.

video.description: Freshman Guard Tyler Perkins scored a game-high 19 points with five three-points in Penn's 80-51 win over Dartmouth.

article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Tyler Perkins scored 19 points to help Pennsylvania defeat Dartmouth 80-51 on Saturday in an Ivy League opener. Perkins added five rebounds for the Quakers (9-7). Andrew Laczkowski scored 10 points while finishing 4 of 6 from the floor, and added six rebounds. Reese McMullen had 10 points and shot 4 for 6, including 2 for 4 from beyond the arc. Ryan Cornish finished with 17 points for the Big Green (4-10). Dartmouth also got 13 points from Jayden Williams. Brandon Mitchell-Day also had three points, six rebounds and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
